title: Tsukuyomi: Moon Phase Special
synopsis: Omake Special from the final DVD volume. The Special storyline has very little to do with the original series outside of having some of the same characters, and has a completely different storyline which does not fit into anything which came before it.
staff: [['Shinbou, Akiyuki', ['Director']], ['Tamura, Koutarou', ['Episode Director']], ['Fukunaga, Gen', ['Executive Producer']], ['Arima, Keitarou', ['Original Creator']]]
